OL,7,FThe family of a pensioner stabbed to
OL,8,Fdeath by a mental health patient have
OL,9,Fsaid their lives have changed forever
OL,10,Fas they call for a full public enquiry
OL,11,Fto stop it happening again.
OL,13,FIn August 2023, 74-year-old Roger
OL,14,FLeadbeater was stabbed 76 times by
OL,15,FEmma Borowy as he walked his dog in a
OL,16,FSheffield Park.
