OL,7,FBorowy had absconded from leave from
OL,8,Fan acute mental health unit in Bolton,
OL,9,FGreater Manchester. She was charged
OL,10,Fwith his murder but died in prison
OL,11,Ffour months later.
OL,13,FHis killing has stayed with his family.
OL,15,FRoger's niece, Angela Hector, said:
OL,16,F"To meet your end in that way, he
OL,17,Fdidn't take his last breath and fade
OL,18,Faway, he had grazes where he'd tried
OL,19,Fto get away from her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
