OL,7,F"He had 124 injuries, she'd damaged
OL,8,Fevery organ in his body. So he knew he
OL,9,Fwas going to die and he tried to fight
OL,10,Fher off. And to hear that about your
OL,11,Floved one how they met their end, it
OL,12,Fwas just absolutely horrific."
OL,14,FRoger was a retired bus driver for
OL,15,Fchildren with special educational
OL,16,Fneeds.
OL,18,FShe described her late uncle as loved
OL,19,Fby the community.
