OL,7,F''Everyone in the community knew him
OL,8,Fcos he loved nothing more that to stop
OL,9,Fand talk. He was a assive support for
OL,10,Fmy other daughter Kerry and her
OL,11,Fdisabled child and partner.''
OL,13,FOn Thursday a coroner ruled the
OL,14,Fpensioner was unlawfully killed.
OL,16,FRoger's family believe clear signs
OL,17,Fabout Ms Borowy's behaviour were
OL,18,Fmissed.
