OL,7,FThe 32-year-old had openly admitted to
OL,8,Fbeing obsessed with witchcraft and the
OL,9,Fdevil.
OL,11,FAn inquest into Roger's death heard
OL,12,Fhow she was sectioned after she was
OL,13,Farrested for killing two goats.
OL,15,FMs Borowy had repeatedly assaulted
OL,16,Fstaff in the secure ward she was being
OL,17,Fcared for and had twice escaped by
OL,18,Fsmashing windows.
