OL,7,FPolice found her on a train to
OL,8,FSheffield with knives and a hammer.
OL,9,FOfficers noted she'd threatened a
OL,10,F'bloodbath' and made threats to kill.
OL,12,FHowever none of this information was
OL,13,Fpassed on to NHS staff by either
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police or South
OL,15,FYorkshire Police.
OL,17,FAngela said she is "disgusted"
OL,18,Finformation isn't shared between
OL,19,Fauthorities.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
