OL,7,FDays before Roger's murder, Ms Borowy
OL,8,Fwas granted leave by a doctor who had
OL,9,Fnever met her.
OL,11,FAt the conclusion of the inquest, the
OL,12,Fcoroner, Tanyka Rawden, said the
OL,13,Fpatient's leave request would probably
OL,14,Fhave been rejected if procedures had
OL,15,Fbeen followed.
OL,17,FThe thought that someone with mental
OL,18,Fhealth issues and history can be
OL,19,Freleased and go on to kill still
OL,20,Fhaunts the family.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
