OL,7,FHis grand-niece, Ellie, said: "You
OL,8,Flook at everybody differently. It
OL,9,Faffects us trying to take my dog out.
OL,10,FI can't allow myself to cos you don't
OL,11,Fthink you're going to come back. We're
OL,12,Fnot the same people we were two and a
OL,13,Fhalf years ago."
OL,15,FThe coroner criticised the procedures
OL,16,Fof both Greater Manchester and South
OL,17,FYorkshire police forces when dealing
OL,18,Fwith handovers of vulnerable missing
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
