OL,7,FA Prevention of Future Deaths (PFD)
OL,8,Freport has been issued to both forces,
OL,9,Fmeaning they must take action to
OL,10,Fprevent further deaths from happening.
OL,12,FHowever Angela believes Coroner's
OL,13,FCourts don't have the power to enforce
OL,14,Fchange - only to advise it.
OL,16,FShe's now written to the Department of
OL,17,FHealth asking for more drastic action.
