OL,7,F''Some deaths some murders get
OL,8,Findependent inquiries. Who determines
OL,9,Fthat value of life? Roger had the
OL,10,Fright to life equally - as anyone
OL,11,Felse.''
OL,13,FHis great niece, Lisa Hammond, added:
OL,14,F''These systems that keep failing,
OL,15,Fpeople are losing their lives. It's
OL,16,Fthe same story. Known to services,
OL,17,Fmental health issues.''
