OL,7,FAlmost 400 patients treated by mental
OL,8,Fhealth services in England killed or
OL,9,Fwere suspected of killing someone
OL,10,Fbetween 2018 and 2023.
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Mental Health Trust
OL,13,Fhas said it has "learned lessons" at
OL,14,Fprevious inquests.
OL,16,FBoth Greater Manchester Police and
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire Police accepted the
OL,18,F"learning opportunities" and committed
OL,19,Fto making improvements in monitoring
OL,20,Fand handover processes.
